:{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34999,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/19\/extravagant-food-clothing\/","url_meta":{"origin":15133,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Luxury: Worst Muslims extravagant in food, clothing, speech","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere will be men from my nation who eat a variety of foods, drink a variety of drinks, wear a variety of clothes, and are boastful in their speech. These are the worst of my nation.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15161,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/21\/prophet-sometimes-green\/","url_meta":{"origin":15133,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Clothes: Permission to wear green clothing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Rimthah reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, wearing two green cloaks. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2812 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0631\u0650\u0645\u0652\u062b\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u064f\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e